{"tid":300694,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【咁樣嘅喂】出前一丁清仔變大人 崩壞了定靚仔咗？","createTime":"2017-06-28T06:22:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-28T12:40:11.000Z","uid":26332,"like":79,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"196f22853cf197245dd75fb2e64816bf2baafd3d","tid":300694,"uid":26332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T06:22:33.000Z","msg":"「出前一丁麻油麵&hellip;&hellip;出前一丁麻油麵&hellip;呀&hellip;出前一丁麻牛麵吖唔該！」有番咁上下年紀嘅香港人，應該都會對以上廣告有點印象。出前一丁大家由細食到大，包裝上面嘅清仔就由細睇到大。雖然一般人都唔會想睇到卡通人物變老，但品牌總係鍾意搞搞新意思。繼2015年搵日本男星速水直道化身真人版清仔後，日清最近就發佈咗一條新廣告，畫出漫畫版長大了的清仔。<br />\n<br />\n根據官方形象，長大了的清仔「高大俊俏」，「在香港街頭跳舞，圍觀的人深深被他吸引」，配合「靚仔棒丁麵」新口味登場。不過部份網民對於唔再可愛，仲有陣花輪同學自戀味嘅成人清仔就似乎唔多受落。<br />\n記者：李珮禎<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/supplement/20170628/56886340\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fsupplement%2F20170628%2F56886340&d=anOzd1FYTW2EZ%2B0L9%2Fb%2F9Mn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=7a6c322c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fsupplement%2F20170628%2F56886340&h=fa3913bb\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/supplement/20170628/56886340</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個新廣告笑死我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n附上廣告link: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O8UivDlFQLg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DO8UivDlFQLg&d=anOzd1FYTW2EZ%2B0L9%2Fb%2F9Mn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=ec18c9a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O8UivDlFQLg</a>"},{"pid":"4b7b9256fc16c16537976fab23bc95edf2910f78","tid":300694,"uid":26332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T06:25:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e801c8af98a387720ab9